snippet.textDisplay: I did a little observation on the cat, I think the cat is an SCP object numbered 1316, named Lucy. SCP-1316 is to be the only SCP object contained at Bio Containment Site 39. it is meant to be a cat-shaped spy. While been in Foundation custody 1316 had free access to many sites, and had seen many other objects that were kept at the site. So I think the reason for Rick and Jerrys' breakdown is because some objects at the SCP foundation were too... nasty looking, or too indescribable. Rick told the cat to go away at the end is because he is afraid that the foundation will find him, but that's also the reason why the cat was there- to find protection.
